  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are not alone. But the voices say you are. He left something behind — in the walls, in the noise, in you. The house remembers. The tapes won’t stop. And the Father… he’s still fading.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3716850/extras/de730424eaf89a0f8fe0919316c2a8d7.poster.avif?t=1748774430\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3716850/extras/de730424eaf89a0f8fe0919316c2a8d7.webm?t=1748774430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3716850/extras/de730424eaf89a0f8fe0919316c2a8d7.mp4?t=1748774430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3716850/extras/7526a17edfe139919ed8e5e316da3d19.poster.avif?t=1748774430\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3716850/extras/7526a17edfe139919ed8e5e316da3d19.webm?t=1748774430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3716850/extras/7526a17edfe139919ed8e5e316da3d19.mp4?t=1748774430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3716850/extras/a71db49124c578855abcbc356cfb1206.poster.avif?t=1748774430\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3716850/extras/a71db49124c578855abcbc356cfb1206.webm?t=1748774430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3716850/extras/a71db49124c578855abcbc356cfb1206.mp4?t=1748774430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Duration: ~ 30 min</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dead Tapes: Fading Father is a first-person psychological horror experience that plunges you into the collapsing mind of a man consumed by addiction and fading memories. Uncover disturbing tapes, navigate twisted hallucinations, and witness a slow descent into madness where the line between reality and nightmare is long gone.</p>",
